summary: The moviepage14.html file contributes to the system by presenting a webpage dedicated to a specific movie, "How to Train Your Dragon." The file includes HTML elements for displaying the movie title, poster, summary, and a trailer. Additionally, it features a rating system implemented with star icons that users can interact with to submit their ratings for the movie. The file also includes links to other pages in the system, such as the homepage, about page, and contact page, accessible through a hamburger menu. Overall, this file introduces the functionality for users to view movie details and submit ratings within the software system.
